title: IS_TRACK_SWITCHED_OFF
content:
0xE0C53765// IsTrackSwitchedOff
bool IS_TRACK_SWITCHED_OFF(int track);Parameters:track: The track id (between 0 - 27)Returns: If this track allows ambient trains to spawnGetter for SWITCH_TRAIN_TRACK. Determines if ambient trains are able to spawn on this track.
